6","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4364,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/07\/worship-all-night-in-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":34167,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Worship: The Prophet only worships all night in Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 7, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: I have not known the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, to read the entire Quran in a single night, nor to spend the whole night in prayer until the morning, nor to spend an entire month in fasting, except during the month of Ramadan.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28106,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/23\/allah-has-waived-fasting-half-of-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":34167,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Travel: Allah has waived fasting, half of prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 23, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Amr ibn Umayyah reported: I came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, from a journey and he said, \u201cStay to eat, O Abu Umayyah.\u201d I said, \u201cIndeed, I am fasting.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cCome close to me and I will tell you about the traveler.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/cate